{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it illegal to require guarantors for tenants in receipt of housing benefit ",
        "additional_details": "We applied for a property and we were required to get a guarantor because we are in receipt of housing benefit. At our age of 47, getting a guarantor isn\u2019t an option and we feel that we have been indirectly discriminated against. We know we\u2019re not the only people in this position.",
        "background": "The Government should help end indirect discrimination against tenants on housing benefit by making it illegal to require a guarantor to rent a property when you are in receipt of housing benefit.",
